precis:
Amendments to the FRESH FRUIT AND VEGETABLE REGULATIONS which eliminate
the compulsory requirement for an inspection of all produce in the import,
export or interprovincial trade, other than for apples, blueberries, field
tomatoes, onions and potatoes.
